data.description: This single family home has 3 bedrooms, one bath, ready for a new homeowner, new interior paint and carpet, central air and heat. Fenced front yard, large backyard with a lemon tree!  Located in East San Jose, walking distance to schools, easy access to shopping, restaurants, freeways and Prusch Park.  With a little TLC you can make this house into your forever home!
